name: PDFDestination
desc: A PDFDestination object describes a point on a PDF page.

items.name: var page: PDFPage?
items.desc: Returns the page that the destination refers to.

items.name: var point: CGPoint
items.desc: Returns the point, in page space, that the destination refers to.

items.name: func compare(PDFDestination) -> ComparisonResult
items.desc: Returns a comparison result that indicates the location of the destination in the document, relative to the current position.
